Title: [BOUNTY][Charity] IoTeX - A Decentralized Network for Internet of Things (IoT)
Body: IoTeX General AMA — November 9, 2018 "We are back with our next bi-weekly AMA which will be a GENERAL one this Friday, November 9, 2018 from 11:00 AM to 1:00 PM PST. Author: cryptoaxela
Title: [BOUNTY][Charity] IoTeX - A Decentralized Network for Internet of Things (IoT)
Body: IoTeX (Blockchain) A decentralized network for Internet of Things (IoT) powered by a privacy-centric blockchain.  IoTeX is the next generation of the IoT-oriented blockchain platform with vast scalability, privacy, isolatability, and developability for incubating new IoT applications and ecosystems. Connecting the physical world, block by block. Total Token Supply (fixed): 10,000,000,000, IOTX Private Sale (closed): 25,000,  ETH Token Price: 1 IOTX = 0.0000125 ETH  Website: https://iotex.io/ Telegram: https://iotex.io/telegram Twitter: https://twitter.com/iotex_io  About IoTeX - https://medium.com/iotex/why-we-created-iotex-5c3124420b20 Blockchains for the IoT - https://medium.com/iotex/blockchains-for-the-iot-c4d828b5a9ed  Bounty program  - https://iotex.io/community-reward Charity Program - https://medium.com/iotex/announcement-iotex-charity-program-b9d71709bdcb (Whitelist registration starts on 3/13/2018 10AM PST & ends on 3/16/2018 10AM PST.)   Steps to Participate Bounty program:    Answer:  1. What is IoTeX’s role in the blockchain ecosystem? * A decentralized platform of privacy-centric blockchain for various vendors to build DApps for IoT (3)  2. Among IoTeX's four innovations, which one represents the key architecture? Blockchain in Blockchains (4)  3. Which of the following is not a use case described in the IoTeX Whitepaper? Social Network Platform Integration (1)  4. Who can you contact to participate in IoTeX's community reward program? @IoTeXBountyBot in Telegram (3)  5. When can I exchange my points to IOTX token? Within 15 days after IOTX token issuance (4)
